Extension triggers on a page matching the following URL: http://localhost:8001/*
It reads "config" file in its directory and copies content to clipboard.
Each time you visit k8s login page just press CTRL+V to insert a token into the input.

Installation
1. Create a symbolic link in the extension directory pointing to ~/.kube/config (ln -s ~/.kube/config config)
2. Open Chrome, go to chrome://extensions
3. Ensure "Developer mode" is on and select "Load unpacked extension..."
4. Select this extension and enjoy
